item.title: CVE-2021-36175|2024-08-04T00:47:43.815Z -- fortinet -- fortinet%20fortiwebmanager
item.description: An improper neutralization of input vulnerability [CWE-79] in FortiWebManager versions 6.2.3 and below, 6.0.2 and below may allow a remote authenticated attacker to inject malicious script/tags via the name/description/comments parameter of various sections of the device.
